	<string>HeyCaby needs access to your camera to take profile photos, taxi photos, and upload documents.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>HeyCaby Driver needs your location while you are online or on an active ride to show your position to nearby riders, receive ride requests, update pickup progress, and support navigation even if the app is briefly in the background.</string>
	<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>HeyCaby Driver needs your location while you use the app to show the map, receive nearby ride requests, update pickup progress, and support navigation.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription</key>
	<string>HeyCaby Driver needs your location while you are online or on an active ride to show your position to nearby riders, receive ride requests, update pickup progress, and support navigation even if the app is briefly in the background.</string>
	<key>NSFaceIDUsageDescription</key>
	<string>HeyCaby gebruikt Face ID om een veilige dienstwissel (Secure Shift Handover) te bevestigen.</string>
	<key>NSPhotoLibraryUsageDescription</key>
	<string>HeyCaby needs access to your photo library to select profile photos, taxi photos, and upload documents.</string>
	<key>UIApplicationSceneManifest</key>
	<dict>
		<key>UIApplicationSupportsMultipleScenes</key>
		<false/>
